README for SpaceFM Mount-Tools plugin v0.2

AUTHOR
  Tri Le <trile7 at gmail dot com>

DEPENDENCIES
  Required: mnttools, smbclient
  Optional: yad - display trayicon
  Optional: lsof - list open files

INSTALL
  Follow SpaceFM plugin installation here http://ignorantguru.github.com/spacefm/spacefm-manual-en.html#plugins-install

DESCRIPTION
  Browse and mount Samba/Windows share.  You'll be ask to enter username and password (leave password blank if you don't want it save in history).  You can choose to browse for server on network or enter server name/ip manually, and then choose a share folder.

